videos.description: UNC students hold up "Boo-Yah" signs and rep Stuart Scott t-shirts during the Tar Heels' game vs. Ohio State.

videos.description: Brandon Robinson comes out of nowhere and delivers a monster block on Ohio State in the first half.
videos.headline: Robinson puts up monster block

videos.headline: Anthony hits back-to-back 3s
